       S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN.

           INITIALIZE        WK-AREA
                             WK-SYSIN
                             WK-CNT

      *    JCL SYSIN ACCEPT
           ACCEPT  WK-SYSIN  FROM    SYSIN

           DISPLAY '*------------------------------------------*'
           DISPLAY '* BJL0040 PGM START                        *'
